show.description: Stock market la panam sambathikirathu eppadi nu neraiya edathula solli kodukkuranga ! Sila per panam vaangittu paid tips laam kooda kodukkuranga, but antha tips, ideas laam thodarnthu palan tharathu illa. Sila neram workout aagum, pala neram failure aaidum. Kastapattu sambathicha panatha loss pannaama Stock market la thodarnthu laabam sambathikanum na athukku neenga follow panna vendiya visayangal enna nu therinjukanumaa ? appo intha audio book ka kelunga.
